  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Lorry Crane Driver Cum Operator",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Description</strong></u></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>1. Operate lorry crane in safe manner.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>2. Able to operate lorry crane with bucket.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>3. Perform basic maintenance and upkeeping of vehicle, daily routine inspection of crane safety devices, </p>\n<p>    load indicators in good, clean and safe conditions before and after any lifting operations.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>4. Having experience in tree pruning works will be an advantage.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>5. Able to assist in loading and unloading of plants, soil, materials and machinery.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>6. Able to carry out tree pruning and tree cutting works.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>7. Manage worker from tree cutting / tree pruning team.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>8. Other ad-hoc duties as assigned by Supervisor.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>9. Be reliable, responsible and good team player.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>10. Comply with all road safety, traffic regulations, safe workpractices, site safety.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>11. Report any issues or repair needed.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Job Requirements</strong></u></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>1. Possess a valid Singapore Driving Licence Class 4 / Class 5.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>2. Possess WSQ certificate in Lorry crane operation.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>3. Must have a clean driving track records.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>4. Having minimum 3 years of lorry crane driving experience in carrying out tree pruning and tree cutting works.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>5. Good communication skills with worker and client.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>6. Able to communicate basic English.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>7. Be physically fit and hardworking.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Interested canditates can contact us @ HP: 9782 8975</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>",
